{
  "texts": [
    "This study was an initial effort to explore the potential of ChatGPT as a feedback source in the context of essay writing and to compare the extent to which the quality of feedback generated by ChatGPT differs from the feedback provided by peers.",
    "Below we discuss our findings for each research question.",
    "For the first research question, the results revealed a disparity in feedback quality when comparing peer-generated feedback to feedback generated by ChatGPT.",
    "Peer feedback demonstrated higher quality compared to ChatGPT-generated feedback.",
    "This discrepancy is attributed primarily to variations in the descriptive and problem-identification features of the feedback."
  ]
}